title: Andrew WK - Wolf it Out! Vol. 1 & 2
description:
Wolf It Out! Volumes 1 & 2

Courtesy of http://www.dontstopthenoise.com

Here are both volumes of the Andrew WK tribute albums, When In Doubt, Wolf It Out!  There are some kind of crappy songs on here, but if you are an AWK fan and you dig through it, you&#039;ll definitely find some gems.

RIP Andrew WK: 1992-2004
